113
00:07:13.892 --> 00:07:17.601
For a start,
let's talk about content scannability.

114
00:07:17.601 --> 00:07:19.709
As we've already said, right?

115
00:07:19.709 --> 00:07:23.531
Most people do not read your copy,
they scan it.

116
00:07:23.531 --> 00:07:26.373
And so we wanna facilitate that and
enable that and

117
00:07:26.373 --> 00:07:28.887
make our content as scannable as possible.

118
00:07:28.887 --> 00:07:31.610
And there are essentially
two ways we can do this.

119
00:07:31.610 --> 00:07:38.509
One is how we structure our content and
the other is how we write our content.

120
00:07:38.509 --> 00:07:43.392
I'll come to structure in a little bit,
but let's talk about writing your content.

121
00:07:43.392 --> 00:07:44.179
Writing for

122
00:07:44.179 --> 00:07:49.461
the web is different because people
are just scanning through it very quickly.

123
00:07:49.461 --> 00:07:53.635
And that means that it needs
to be incredibly simple and

124
00:07:53.635 --> 00:07:55.730
very easy to scan through.

125
00:07:55.730 --> 00:07:58.393
And there are certain things
we can do to achieve that.

126
00:07:58.393 --> 00:08:04.227
So for example, we can avoid using
jargon or unfamiliar terminology.

127
00:08:04.227 --> 00:08:07.988
But we can also use shorter
sentence structures.

128
00:08:07.988 --> 00:08:12.658
And we can avoid too many adverbs and
things like that.

129
00:08:12.658 --> 00:08:17.337
Now if like me, you're not particularly
good at doing that kind of stuff

130
00:08:17.337 --> 00:08:22.720
naturally, then instead what you can do
is, you can use a tool like Hemingway app.

131
00:08:22.720 --> 00:08:26.024
And Hemingway app is a free
online tool that you can use.

132
00:08:26.024 --> 00:08:28.906
You enter your content into it,
it scans it.

133
00:08:28.906 --> 00:08:32.682
It makes suggestions about how you
can shorten it and improve it and

134
00:08:32.682 --> 00:08:34.107
make it more scannable.

135
00:08:34.107 --> 00:08:36.995
It'll also give you
a readability level and

136
00:08:36.995 --> 00:08:39.736
tell you whether that is good or not good.

137
00:08:39.736 --> 00:08:43.528
So it's a really good sanity checker for
the copy that you write.

138
00:08:43.528 --> 00:08:48.492
And there are other tools out there like
that for example, I use Grammarly a lot.

139
00:08:48.492 --> 00:08:52.724
But what I like about Hemingway app
is that it's very much designed for

140
00:08:52.724 --> 00:08:53.950
reading on the web.

141
00:08:53.950 --> 00:08:56.764
It's quite aggressive
in its suggestions and

142
00:08:56.764 --> 00:09:01.532
