long sentences or lots of conjunctions.

143
00:09:01.532 --> 00:09:04.479
So lots of ands and
commas and things like that.

144
00:09:04.479 --> 00:09:07.740
So just run your draft
copy through that and

145
00:09:07.740 --> 00:09:13.281
you'll find that it'll become a lot
more scannable and easy to digest.

146
00:09:13.281 --> 00:09:18.650
But it's not just about writing in plain
language and being as concise as possible.

