151
00:09:34.631 --> 00:09:40.890
It has to be concise, but
that's two different things, right?

152
00:09:40.890 --> 00:09:46.042
Concise is,
it's got to be as short as it can be and

153
00:09:46.042 --> 00:09:49.007
still get the point across.

154
00:09:49.007 --> 00:09:53.602
And sometimes you need more words
to be able to explain something.

155
00:09:53.602 --> 00:09:56.272
Is just the nature of the beast, right?

156
00:09:56.272 --> 00:09:58.730
And so don't be afraid to do that.

157
00:09:58.730 --> 00:10:02.825
But what you need to avoid is copy that
includes what Steve Kruger in his book,

158
00:10:02.825 --> 00:10:05.098
