00:10:08.314 --> 00:10:11.857
But it's things like hey,
welcome to our site and stuff like that,

161
00:10:11.857 --> 00:10:14.856
which just doesn't help
answer anybody's questions.

162
00:10:14.856 --> 00:10:16.513
See, remove that kind of thing.

163
00:10:16.513 --> 00:10:18.065
And also remove repetition.

164
00:10:18.065 --> 00:10:21.518
So when we're trying to convince
somebody in an argument,

165
00:10:21.518 --> 00:10:25.729
